1. *Popis* stanovništva se sprovodi svake desete godine. (The *census* is conducted every ten years.) 
2. Za popisivanje inventara smo angažovali spoljnu firmu. (We hired an external company to take inventory.) 
3. *Popis* zaliha se radi na kraju svakog meseca. (Inventory *check* is done at the end of each month.) 
4. Javni *popis* akcionara je dostupan na sajtu kompanije. (The public *register* of shareholders is available on the company's website.) 
5. Poljoprivrednici su morali da urade *popis* stoke na svom gazdinstvu. (Farmers had to do a *count* of livestock on their farms.) 
6. *Popisati* sve stavke na spisku pre kupovine je dobra navika. (Checking off all items on the list before shopping is a good habit.) 
7. Komisija je sprovela *popis* glasova i proglasila pobednika. (The commission conducted a *tally* of votes and declared the winner.) 
8. Povreda igrača je naterala trenera da uradi novi *popis* startera. (The player's injury forced the coach to make a new *selection* of starters.) 
9. Država je uradila *popis* nepokretnosti u cilju utvrđivanja poreza na imovinu. (The state conducted a *listing* of real estate to determine property tax.) 
10. Na *popisu* su bila i imena nekoliko poznatih ličnosti. (The *list* included the names of several famous personalities.)